thread.title: Noela

author: Noela
title: Noela
text:
Easily able to shop online. I tried two stores, Officeworks & Harvey Norman, on foot and they didn't have the product in stock. So I went online; easy to order - Printzone price was the cheapest, easy to pay; immediate response with confirming emails from Printzone & the product was delivered the next day to my door on an island.
Thank you. You will have my next order as well!
